    source sources/gnome-power-manager/${VERSION:0:4}/gnome-power-manager-$VERSION.tar.bz2
  homepage http://www.gnome.org/projects/gnome-power-manager/
  estimate 6600
      desc 'responds to HAL events with user-configurable reactions
Currently it supports UPSs, notebook batteries and AC adapters.'

